tweet: 8c The questions that #digitalsociology is concerned with are drawn from trad'l sociological theory:

name: @JessieNYC
tweet: 8b While #digitalsociology + #dh may use similar tools, #digitalsociology is concerned with a different set of questions.

name: @JessieNYC
tweet: 8a #digitalsociology is concerned with society - and social inequality - as well as culture and cultural critique.

tweet: 8 #digitalsociology is distinct from the #digitalhumanities in a number of ways, ...

name: @JessieNYC
tweet: 7 #digitalsociology is concerned with activism + social change and the ways that digital technologies promote or deter this

tweet: 6 #digitalsociology is concerned with theories of the social world + how these might be re-envisioned in the digital era.

tweet: 5 cont'd #digitalsociology is concerned w/ how those areas are being transformed by the digital era

tweet: 3 #digitalsociology relies on mixed-methods that incorporate both the material, face-to-face and the digital, online

tweet: 2 #digitalsociology is concerned with social inequalities + the ways that digital technologies may exacerbate or ameliorate these
